items.title: FlutterExplained
items.description: In the year 2019, I started with an ambitious goal to set up a youtube account, create content and writing apps. Now in 2020, I finally manage it and try to improve in all facets of it. This channel should be the Wikipedia for Flutter development and all questions related to Flutter should be able to find an answer here.I am still at the beginning, and I am glad that already 500 viewers found their way to this Youtube Channel, currently, I am working Full Time to make great content and tutorials with Flutter Explained and App Development. With nearly one decade of software development experience and more than 3 years in the design topic, I am the right one to help you with your problems.So if you have any questions related to development or flutter, reach out to me and contact me on https://twitter.com/max_myracle!

items.title: Mahmud Ahsan

I have over 30 personal iOS apps in the Apple app store which downloaded over 13 Million times from the app store.
